snippet.title: More Ore - The Incremental RPG Trailer
snippet.description:
The idle incremental game of your dreams... if you dream about ores. Do whatever it takes to mine More Ore while conquering the world in your spare time.

Wishlist the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1916800/More_Ore__The_Incremental_Idle_RPG/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/NU99mMQ
Play the beta version: https://syns.studio/more-ore?youtube
